{"tid":1764459,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醒少少咪再犯低級錯誤呀！","createTime":"2019-12-01T06:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T06:47:02.000Z","uid":72515,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16689884883d1302fdd0e8bee1db74136ac170d6","tid":1764459,"uid":72515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"雖然已經過咗咁多個月，好多嘢都已經有人提過<br />\n但由於仲係好多人有呢類問題（可能不斷有新手加入？），所以我畫嚟再提醒下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎隨便share<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VJNLiv5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVJNLiv5.jpg&h=6bc3e444&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3825bi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3825bi.jpg&h=cc253517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbhrNp5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbhrNp5.jpg&h=c8998ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">決定好幾時online幾時offline，換裝要徹底</span><br />\nonline時包實啲咪唔怕被影到，亦唔駛搞到要打爛人哋舖頭啲CCTV增加民怨；<br />\noffline後就唔好繼續全身黑喇，好易被target，除非你志在做被捕師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純黑連帽風褸係好物👍🏻 全身盡量唔好有Logo，背囊同鞋最好笠返個套<br />\n眼罩最好黐反光紙，耳仔同染過嘅頭髮一定要遮<br />\n戴返個腰包裝貴重嘢，咁就萬一背囊被捉時都可以棄背囊逃走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/01/140925_bb4c00171a497ca2df0dcc869cb1d3d1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F01%2F140925_bb4c00171a497ca2df0dcc869cb1d3d1.jpeg&h=d4ce42b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gPGswTh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgPGswTh.jpg&h=ae3af958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1）Roadblock</span><br />\nSet rb唔好見人set你就set，要思考清楚<br />\nrb應係警渣最有可能到達嘅位置&amp;警渣防線前<br />\n如果完全未見警渣蹤影就最好睇住哨兵消息先再作決定（當然可以準備定材料備用）<br />\n如果set錯喺人群中間/撤退路線就會妨礙自己人逃生，亦可能導致kick親而被捉甚至人踩人<br />\n唔好因為「想幫手做啲嘢」就亂set rb<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2）留返中間</span><br />\n中間要留一條通道方便人上前線&amp;畀前線走<br />\n如果有前線急用嘅物資，就跑中間通道交上去，唔好再用物資人鏈慢慢傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3）企疏啲</span><br />\n當情況開始緊張時，要企疏啲（可以拖實同伴但同其他人要保持一定距離），方便撤退<br />\n物資人鏈要隔一個手位，唔好「為做嘢而做嘢」見夠人都夾硬塞入去，好多時愈多人效率愈慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24f09776742131dfaf730d2129a0e082f524a82","tid":1764459,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:32:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"436e9f0cb9c2658765088479d73b26539ec4cd8a","tid":1764459,"uid":51422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d26ae9ef2b2a1304c44429ddd78b4887d0c8ce1c","tid":1764459,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fdfc75f0103f7108112c23dfc74d158f7baa90","tid":1764459,"uid":72515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/01/143126_bed94cf35d401969407612e8a907bea2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F01%2F143126_bed94cf35d401969407612e8a907bea2.jpeg&h=b7f4c2ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實「有狗」係一句廢話，周圍都有狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傳訊要盡量清晰準確<br />\n認一認唔同警車種類、警渣種類、出門前睇一睇地圖，真係好基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hkhSH7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhkhSH7c.jpg&h=555bacfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qA5iFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qA5iFS.jpg&h=4c43cd65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多手足都好大隻同有高級gear，而且小隊內要用walkie通訊（現場收唔到電話是常識吧）<br />\n唔好亂咁捉鬼，隨時破壞小隊行動同害手足被捕/被攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有懷疑就觀察多陣&amp;問下先，唔好單憑外表判斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gBrHkUO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgBrHkUO.jpg&h=24fa79ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留意周遭環境，當氣氛開始緊張（如：防暴已落地/有人受傷）<br />\n就唔好再嗌口號/唱歌，以免妨礙重要訊息傳播<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6xfFVu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6xfFVu.jpg&h=3a2da085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（湊熱鬧畫隻靜靜雞先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n回程時可能會好多嘢忍唔住同同伴傾，但周圍都可能有便衣，要傾就text msg啦<br />\n記得就算喺家長車或者黃店都唔好講online經歷呀！<br />\n現場亦都可能有鬼，唔好大大聲講之前online經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺網上分享都要小心衡量風險，唔好亂po相打咭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毋忘初心，繼續革命<br />\n</span></span><br />\n等間見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6864bb93bd20b1379cfc17d9822bc4b3bd4bddfe","tid":1764459,"uid":261287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:47:02.000Z","msg":"P 牌無力推"}]}